{"data":[{"date":"11:28 10/07","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/20/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Singapore, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bu\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><h2>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-Hoang-Anh-Tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-U19-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n sau khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1edfi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Indonesia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, trong khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 Singapore c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u00e9m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Qua gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c CLB \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng nh\u00ec. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Qatar tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2019.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190804.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 to\u00e0n thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (KT): Chia tay gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 trong n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 to\u00e0n thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4102","checkdouble":"190845"},{"date":"09:05 10/07","title":"M.U \u0111i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Milinkovic-Savic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mu-di-them-mot-buoc-nua-o-thuong-vu-chieu-mo-milinkovicsavic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Man United m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi m\u1edf ra hi v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Italia cho Lazio.</h2><h2>M.U c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sang \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ee5&nbsp;Milinkovic-Savic&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Lazio-muon-mua-Aaron-Ramsey-thay-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sang \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 phi v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang Italia \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o ti\u1ebfng \u00dd Il Messaggero&nbsp;ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a M.U cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Milinkovic-Savic v\u1ec1 Bernabeu. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergej Milinkovic-Savic n\u0103m nay ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Savic s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng (1m91), c\u00f3 k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1eabn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap anh thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Seria A nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lazio, Claudio Lotito \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1eaft khe khi ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Savic ra \u0111i khi nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 155 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4101","checkdouble":"190819"},{"date":"11:16 10/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Anh r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1 1 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ecf \u00e1o s\u1ed1 33 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u00e1o nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i khi anh ra m\u1eaft Bayer Leverkusen, 19 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Santi Cazorla, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBernd Leno v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi Petr Cech r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Petr Cech m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho c\u1ef1u sao Bayer Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno\" title=\"Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Leno \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7. HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Leno b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f2n Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c David Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4100","checkdouble":"190840"},{"date":"07:44 10/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7: 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-107-48-gio-nua-ronaldo-se-la-nguoi-cua-juve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea t\u00ednh \"h\u1edbt tay tr\u00ean\" m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Man City. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Tuttosport, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n Maurizio Sarri, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge thay Antonio Conte. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Chelsea tin \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo Sky Sports, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Cristiano Ronaldo sang Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Jorge Mendes v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid, Florentino Perez s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern. </strong>Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Pini Zahavi c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Ba Lan, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho Lewy c\u0169ng v\u01a1i b\u1edbt. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern ph\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u00e2n binh Juventus m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Ronaldo n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. </strong>Emre Can m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. Juve m\u1edbi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. </strong>Raheem Sterling \u0111ang nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Eric Dier v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao Man City nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh. Anh tin c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Sterling l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling\" title=\"Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bo-doi-huyen-thoai-mu-bao-ve-sao-man-city-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u1ee3i khen c\u00e1ch Sterling \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xavi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui. </strong>Vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xavi, anh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</strong> Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4099","checkdouble":"190814"},{"date":"06:47 10/07","title":"Hazard: \u201cT\u1edbi Real Madrid l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hazard-toi-real-madrid-la-giac-mo-cua-moi-cau-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. Gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i cho Real l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u01b0a Hazard v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i St Petersburg. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1ed1 1 l\u00e0 Brazil trong s\u1ef1 kinh ng\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. V\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c cao, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean Hazard l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Real-Madrid-voi-su-nguong-mo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Hazard \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Cristiano Ronaldo (chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang Real m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Zinedine Zidane, m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Zidane \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Los Blancos sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda t\u1edbi Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3m \u0111i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Zidane?&rdquo;, Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean beIN SPORTS. &ldquo;Zidane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Real l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Zidane hay kh\u00f4ng Zidane, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o m\u00e0u xanh c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y phi\u1ec1n n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111ang l\u00e0 World Cup. Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 l\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-tan-cong-co-the-the-cho-ronaldo-tai-real-madrid-180-190789.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\">Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4098","checkdouble":"190811"},{"date":"07:04 10/07","title":"Luis Enrique l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michel Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique sau khi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 La Roja kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Enrique ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0110T TBN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLuis Enrique thay th\u1ebf Fernando Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1m ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, RFEF \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui do nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Luis-Enrique-len-DT-TBN.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salgado \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Enrique</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Michel Salgado c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Luis Enrique c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u201d, Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a FIFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEnrique \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Barcelona v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0103n 3, l\u00e0 HLV t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng Hierro trong 2 ng\u00e0y, Enrique c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4097","checkdouble":"190812"},{"date":"07:25 10/07","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Real Madrid b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho M.U v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/sao-tre-real-madrid-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-va-cac-dai-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United hay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i cho Espanyol d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n (2015/16) v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Marco Asensio \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Anh t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Asensio xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf 53 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Real tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAsensio ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 7 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Qua \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e0ng trai 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Marco-Asensio-se-o-lai-Real-Madrid-thay-vi-toi-cac-dai-gia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00cdt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ea1i gia bao g\u1ed3m Man United, Liverpool, Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Asensio. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac Real t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Marco Asensio. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Asensio th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Horacio Gaggioli l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Asensio\" title=\"tien ve Asensio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tien-ve-Asensio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMarco Asensio s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u\u201d, Gaggioli n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Calciomercato. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n theo th\u1eddi gian. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf Madrid.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec1u. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Los Blancos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Asensio. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 anh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean t\u1ea7m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Real. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Asensio v\u1edbi B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi t\u1eadn n\u0103m 2023 sau l\u1ea7n gia h\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-toi-real-madrid-la-giac-mo-cua-moi-cau-thu-421-190811.html\">Hazard: \u201cT\u1edbi Real Madrid l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-tan-cong-co-the-the-cho-ronaldo-tai-real-madrid-180-190789.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-tranh-gianh-milinkovicsavic-voi-mu-172-190704.html\">Real Madrid tranh gi\u00e0nh Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4096","checkdouble":"190813"},{"date":"08:42 10/07","title":"Sao Man Utd c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/18/sao-man-utd-co-tinh-choc-gian-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nemanja Matic c\u1ed1 \u00fd tr\u00e1i l\u1eddi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Serbia b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Khi \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Serbia n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f9a r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Nemanja Matic s\u1edbm tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Man Utd \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao MU Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao MU Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/matic-da-co-keo-voi-man-utd-tu-khi-con-la-quan-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n khi Serbia b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 Brazil v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean Matic \u0111\u00fang th\u1eadt s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 b\u00ean \u00f4ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i vui v\u1ebb chia s\u1ebb anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u201cch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft ra sao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Matic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mourinho: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng? \u1eea th\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00e1i l\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed5i gi\u1eadn. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Serbia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 Mourinho lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u0103m nay, Man Utd s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean ICC, \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ba \u00f4ng l\u1edbn l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 AC Milan (25/7), Liverpool (28/7) v\u00e0 Real Madrid (31/7).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/131008-lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-icc-2018-ket-qua-international-champions-cup-279-190766.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 - K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 International Champions Cup</span><br>\r\nBongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 International Champions Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi 18 CLB tham d\u1ef1 t\u1eeb 21/7 \u0111\u1ebfn 12/8</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4095","checkdouble":"190826"},{"date":"20:50 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 9/7: \"Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/diem-tin-toi-97-kylian-mbappe-xung-gianh-qua-bong-vang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 9/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 10 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Daniel Fuzato (21 tu\u1ed5i) t\u1eeb Palmeiras v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 97 Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 97 Kylian Mbappe x\u1ee9ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-World-Cup-Cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-Pogbappe-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard cho r\u1eb1ng Kylian Mabppe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng cao qu\u00fd. Ch\u00ednh Mabppe g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 trao gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia, Fabien Delph cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau ph\u00fat n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 mong ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jordan Henderson c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Jamie Vardy c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">BTC ASIAD 2018 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0a hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eafng Sime Vrsaljko trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Anh. Vrsaljko d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nga \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Beckham l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling sau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Becks cho r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o m\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3ng 3.000 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua bia cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Slavonski Brod khi h\u1ecd t\u1eadp trung \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Croatia.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-190800.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/ever-banega-nut-thao-go-cho-messi-392-190799.html\">Ever Banega: N\u00fat th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 cho Messi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/mario-fernandes-hero-never-to-zero-392-190797.html\">Mario Fernandes: Hero never to zero</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/giac-mo-hoang-duong-cua-benjamin-pavard-389-190796.html\">Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 hoang \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Benjamin Pavard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe-180-190795.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\">Mandzukic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4094","checkdouble":"190801"},{"date":"18:10 09/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-tan-cong-co-the-the-cho-ronaldo-tai-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Real trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 li\u1ec7u khi anh ra \u0111i, li\u1ec7u Los Blancos c\u00f3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf CR7.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 10 n\u0103m chinh chi\u1ebfn cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, ng\u00e0y \u00e0m Ronaldo chia tay Real c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o l\u1edbn \u1edf c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch Ronaldo s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB Juventus t\u1eeb m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.</p>\r\n<h2>Inaki Williams - Athletic Bilbao</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng minh, Inaki Williams \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Athletic Bilbao t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 cho t\u1edbi nay, Inaki Williams \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 163 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 34 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1994 khi anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi 54 tr\u1eadn cho Bilbao v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 10 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Inaki Williams l\u00e0 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song gi\u00e1 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u00edt h\u01a1n con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0a Inaki Williams v\u1ec1 Bernabeu, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m qua 5 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/21/Diem-qua-5-ngoi-sao-co-the-the-cho-Ronaldo-tai-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Inaki Williams \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronald</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Robert Lewandowski - FC Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trong su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 29, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ba Lan chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, do \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Los Blancos.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 bao nhi\u00eau cho Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niem hy vong so mot cua DT Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im tieng trong tran dau nay.\" title=\"Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trong su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Edinson Cavani - PSG</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Cavani ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. Cavani c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh h\u01a1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Madrid.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba qua, Cavani \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 40 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn cho PSG. \u0110\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng Ronaldo. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Cavani c\u0169ng t\u1eebng n\u00f3i mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean Cavani n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 sang tu\u1ed5i 31 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 'm\u1eb7n' trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a PSG.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Cavani\" title=\"tien dao Cavani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/nguoi-phap-lo-ngai-dna-phong-ngu-cua-uruguay.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cavani \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Eden Hazard - Chelsea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 Ronaldo tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Hazard l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, Hazard ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real xoay quanh nh\u1eefng m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Bale, Karin Benzema, Marco Asensio,...\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu, Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 chia tay ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p tr\u1eeb khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ed3ng l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil 2010, James Rodriguez 2014, va gio la Eden Hazard 20181\" title=\"Mesut Ozil 2010, James Rodriguez 2014, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Eden Hazard 20181\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/mesut-ozil-2010-james-rodriguez-2014-va-gio-la-eden-hazard-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Eden Hazard 2018 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mauro Icardi - Inter Milan</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 25, Mauro Icardi \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real. V\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CR7, Icardi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m n\u1eefa.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Argentina, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u0169i khoan r\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u00e9n.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Inter Milan thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 l\u1eadn \u0111\u1eadn \u1edf Serie A nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Icardi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"mauro icardi cua Inter\" title=\"mauro icardi cua Inter\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Icardi-muon-o-lai-Inter-Milan-bat-chap-su-quan-tam-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Icardi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid<font face=\"arial, verdana, Lucida Grande, helvetica, sans-serif\">?</font></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-187-190765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-187-190765.html\">5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u00e2y chuy\u1ec1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/modric-khong-tin-ronaldo-se-roi-real-180-190697.html\">Modric kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuu-chu-tich-canh-bao-real-ve-y-dinh-ban-ronaldo-180-190689.html\">C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ramon Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real khi n\u1ea3y sinh \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-190526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-190526.html\">5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu CR7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4093","checkdouble":"190789"},{"date":"18:37 09/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Real chi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/19/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Kylian Mbappe ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Mbappe</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A CR7 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Kylian Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Kylian Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/19/real-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-mbappe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo, h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ra m\u1eaft \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/07 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p CR7 r\u1eddi Bernabeu, Los Blancos s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chi-200-trieu-euro-mua-bom-tan-cua-psg-180-184995.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n mua Mbappe</span> thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 230 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u00a0C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Mbappe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Kylian Mbappe ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kylian Mbappe rat muon chuyen toi Barca\" title=\"Kylian Mbappe r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/20/mbappe-tiet-lo-khong-con-than-tuong-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c quan t\u00e2m Kylian Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Cadena COPE, Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, ngay c\u1ea3 khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Asensio hay Lucas Vazquez s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo l\u00e0 Neymar ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mbappe, Los Blancos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 290 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4092","checkdouble":"190795"},{"date":"20:16 09/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi HLV Fernando Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luis Enrique - HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c khi &quot;La Roja&quot; \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Enrique tro thanh HLV truong DT Tay Ban Nha.\" title=\"Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/chinh-thuc-luis-enrique-tro-thanh-hlv-truong-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi RFEF. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch RFEF Luis Rubiales cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Luis Enrique. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Francisco Molina - t\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a RFEF cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, theo k\u1ecbp xu h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Luis Enrique t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft AS Roma, Celta Vigo v\u00e0 Barcelona. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf c\u00f9ng Barcelona, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2014-15.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Luis Enrique tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">La Roja h\u1ebft s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. RFEF sau \u0111\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro l\u00e0m HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hierro phat bieu sau tran TBN vs Nga\" title=\"Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Fernando Hierro t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Sau khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Fernando Hierro kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0o v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ch\u1ee9c v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, Fernando Hierro c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Francisco Molina Jimenez, m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1c ti\u1ebfp nhi\u1ec7m.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-thoi-ky-den-toi-da-quay-tro-lai-466-190370.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111en t\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro-421-190365.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 r\u1eddi World Cup, L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf HLV Hierro</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4091","checkdouble":"190800"},{"date":"21:56 09/07","title":"R\u1eddi Arsenal, c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/cuu-than-dong-jack-wilshere-den-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ba n\u0103m sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Jack Wilshere, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Wilshere m\u1edbi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \"The Hammers\" v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ba n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/cuu-than-dong-jack-wilshere-den-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Arsenal sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00e1c, Jack Wilshere chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u00f4i m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ea5u West Ham. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd th\u1eddi \u1ea5u th\u01a1 khi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho West Ham, theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Upton Park. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n b\u1edfi gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a West Ham\".</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho Wilshere khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Blackburn th\u00e1ng 9/2008, Wilshere l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Arsenal ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League (16 tu\u1ed5i 256 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Wilshere kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb Arsenal \u0111em cho Bournemouth m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016-17. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wilshere tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 197 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho Arsenal, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 34 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jack-wilshere-ra-mat-doi-bong-moi-trong-24h-toi-172-190477.html\">Jack Wilshere ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi trong 24h t\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-west-ham-172-190460.html\">C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf CLB Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\">Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-sap-toi-fenerbahce-sau-khi-roi-arsenal-172-189936.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Wilshere</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/west-ham-chi-ky-hop-dong-voi-wilshere-neu-172-189534.html\">West Ham ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Wilshere n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi-172-189348.html\">Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4090","checkdouble":"190805"}]}